{
  "name": "RPlog_Imperial_Raid_on_Coruscant",
  "title": "Raid on the Emancipated Imperial Palace",
  "summary": "Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin leads a covert Imperial strike team, including Wescal Cantrell, the pilot Dareus, and Krieg, up through the sewers of the New Republic-held Imperial Palace on Coruscant to steal a datacard pinpointing a Sith planet. Meanwhile the Jedi Johanna senses danger in Palpatine's old throne room, the noble Viktor Faust tours the palace with his bodyguard Phair Kreiss, and NR officers Malika, Tanbris, and the sniper Sandor Woden patrol the halls. When the team's gas grenades and assault erupt into a chaotic firefight, Danik races to the throne room and confronts Johanna, brandishing a hologram of her captured son Etiel to force her surrender. As Malika's marines and reinforcements including Tal'sin, Krieger, and Sandor pour in, Cantrell, Dareus, and Krieg lay down brutal covering fire. Danik drags Johanna into Palpatine's hidden vault, secures the datacard, and reveals he is taking her as a prisoner to the dark planet Ord Trasi; Johanna, desperate to save Etiel, reveals that Warlord Malign is her brother. The Imperials fight their way to a balcony where a YT-2400 waits, with Sandor wounding Cantrell before the strike team escapes with Johanna and the prize, leaving the wounded behind to be tended.",
